Table 1. Crystal data and structure refinement information for compounds 1[^a]

|  |  |
|---|---|
| Empirical formula | C4H3N4O3PbS |
| Formula weight | 394.35 |
| Crystal system | Monoclinic |
| Space group | P2(1)/c |
| a (Å) | 6.9672(9) |
| b (Å) | 13.4568(16) |
| c (Å) | 9.6163(12) |
| α (°) | 90 |
| β (°) | 110.715(2) |
| γ (°) | 90 |
| V (Å³) | 843.30(18) |
| Z | 4 |
| ρ (g/cm³) | 3.106 |
| μ (mm⁻¹) | 20.233 |
| F(000) | 708 |
| Crystal size (mm³) | 0.28×0.24×0.22 |
| θ (°) | 2.72 to 25.02 |
| Limiting indices | |
|  | −8⩽ h ⩽8 |
|  | −16⩽ k ⩽10 |
|  | −10⩽ l ⩽11 |
| Reflections/collected/unique | 4158/1486 [R(int)=0.0354] |
| Data/restraints/parameters | 1486/0/119 |
| Good of fit on F² | 1.101 |
| Final R indices (I >2σ (I)) | R1=0.0244, wR2=0.0618 |

[^a]: R1=Σ||Fo−Fc||/|Fo|, wR2=[Σw(Fo²−Fc²)/Σw(Fo²)]²⁽¹⁄₂⁾.
